short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Show etymology of selected biological and medical terms.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bio Etymology Explorer is a powerful tool designed for students and professionals in the biological and medical fields. This extension provides quick access to the etymology of terms, enhancing your understanding of complex vocabulary. With a focus on a limited selection of words, primarily biological and medical terminology, it helps clarify meanings and origins, making your learning experience more enriching. Discover the roots of language and elevate your studies with Etymology Explorer!
